Source: sky1-npu-dkms
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dkms
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/sky1-linux/sky1-drivers-dkms

Package: sky1-npu-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms
Description: CIX Sky1 Neural Processing Unit driver (DKMS)
 This package provides the AIPU (ARM China Zhouyi NPU) driver
 for the CIX Sky1 NPU using DKMS.
 .
 Hardware: ARM China Zhouyi V3 AIPU with 3 NPU cores
 delivering 30 TOPS (INT8) neural network inference.
 .
 Features: DVFS, per-core power management, DMA buffer support.
